xenon ssh applet use this mindterm applet to log into your xenon account using ssh browsers that support this applet include netscape 4.06 and higher windows and unix and internet explorer 4.0 and higher windows mac os 8 & 9 users must install the macintosh runtime for java plug in for internet explorer the size of the applet is about 600 kbytes so it takes about 3 minutes to download on a 28.8 kb s modem if the applet doesn t appear after revisiting this page try pressing shift reload in your browser in order to use the java ssh applet check that your browser supports java and that java is enabled last updated 23 mar 2003 by ed swierk for comments on this web page only webmaster student cs stanford edu for all other xenon issues can t log in lost password etc action cs stanford edu
